{
  "stem": "7938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because no matter of the account that I give, no matter-- no-- no matter what I-- what you interview me or what I will tell you, it still will not be the same that the future generation can see it on the film.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people ask me sometimes, was it really so bad?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was worse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I say that it was worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In some ways, it was worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was-- there was shooting without limitation and brutality, which you cannot imagine.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If somebody couldn't go, couldn't work, he was knocked to the street with a bayonet, and killed right away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If they wanted to kill any people in the hospital, in the hospital were killed on the spot, because they couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Certain nurses-- and there was for older people a geriatric hospital-- and the-- the nurses apparently gave poison to the-- to the-- to all the-- the old women and old men who were there, because they couldn't even walk out.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And wherever they came in after the liquidation, when they moved already everybody to-- to Plaszow-- not everybody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They moved only to Plaszow whoever could work, or they see that he's young.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But if somebody couldn't, they shot on the-- on the space.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- they shot a doctor at the hospital because he was doing an operation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] On the street, certain soldiers, when they wanted to shoot, and there was a mother with a child, they told her to stay, so that he doesn't have to use more than one bullet.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They should stay in line.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they went through from one house to the other one, and whoever was in the house, they shot there in place where it was, if-- if you didn't run away before.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
